    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_4003286155721751719.png",
                "key": "箱紙切削術",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "箱紙切削術"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">貓箱急件</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">安全運輸護盾</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">貓箱急件</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">綺良良為出戰角色時，我方切換角色後：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>，抽1張牌。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span>（可疊加，最多疊加到2次）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">安全運輸護盾</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>為我方出戰角色提供<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">2點護盾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/e1d9ab13ba19969303b42dbee09f59e7_289405892207434367.png",
                "key": "嗚喵町飛足",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "嗚喵町飛足"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>，在敵方場上生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">貓草豆蔻</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">貓草豆蔻</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所在陣營打出2張行動牌後：</span>對所在陣營的出戰角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/ec58f74c94bbd19ecbb0c33f972f5788_9076736811995520296.png",
                "key": "秘法·驚喜特派",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "秘法·驚喜特派"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_1339809470941012321.png",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_1388556709313847361.png",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_1115657745573183903.png",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1970765117777361828.png",
